The following code is for establishing a monitoring software.
The repliction and testing is done on docker.

vm1: runs a service to generate random number
vm2: runs a service to geenerate random number
vm3: tests whether both services are up and display their content dynamically and if machines are up via ping

Tech Stack : Service1/2 - javascript/Apache
		Monitoring Service : php/Apache

Features: 
1) Dynamiclaly uploads div without refreshing page in html according to response from server
2) Well organized code via docker-compose
3) Alternate bash files are provided for running on individual machines

Running Instructions:
1) For running clone this code and run "bash run.sh"
2) Use the generated ip to open it in your browser
3) For stopping all containers use "docker-compose down" 
